<div id="about-the-community" class="section-spacer">
    <h2 class="sect-title">About Edgewater</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">In the recent years, Edgewater has become a popular choice for residents who wish to get away from the hustle and bustle of the rest of the valley. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">Although a growing community, Edgewater has managed to keep its quiet and serenity and is counted amongst the top communities in the region. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">The average price of Edgewater real estate range between $300,000 and $500,000. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">Green spaces and parks spotting the neighborhood provide ample space for dog-walking, exercising, and relaxing.</p>
        </div>
